title: The Credit Union Christmas 720P WEBRip Adelaide
description: Details At 9:30am on Saturday 18 November 2017, the whistle will blow to signal the beginning of the Credit Union Christmas Pageant! Join more than 260,00 people along the 3.3 kilometre route in Adelaide's city centre to welcome the colourful and exciting Credit Union Christmas Pageant - South Australia's traditional welcome to the festive season. Arrive early to get the best spot along the Pageant route. Watch the amazing parade of storybook floats, listen to the marching bands and wave to Father Christmas. From humble beginnings of just eight horse drawn floats and four bands, the event has grown to include 64 floats and more than 172 moving performing sets. The Credit Union Christmas Pageant is a family event. Come and enjoy the spirit of Christmas and community.
